OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly fine with sunny spells
OL,6,Finitially, but tending to becomes
OL,7,Fcloudier from the northwest through
OL,8,Fthe day, perhaps culminating in late
OL,9,Frain in the west. Very warm and humid.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight
OL,12,Fwith rain in the west at first before
OL,13,Feasing and turning drier and more
OL,14,Fsettled by the morning. Warm and humid
OL,15,Fovernight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FCloudy at first, becoming
OL,18,Fdrier and brighter with some sunny
OL,19,Fspells developing later. Temperatures
OL,20,Fslightly lower than previous days.
OL,21,FWinds light and variable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
