OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,6,Fdrier and brighter with sunny spells
OL,7,Flate, ahead of isolated showers on
OL,8,FMonday. Dry with sunny spells on
OL,9,FTuesday. Temperatures climbing, hot
OL,10,Fand humid.
